    <description>When a contact Joins Onboarding Webinar #3 in Demio, a Zap updates the Billing Call or Webinar Date Completed on the contact which triggers this flow to update the Billing Call or Webinar Date and the Billing Call or Webinar Status to Completed on the Combined Funnel related to the Account and the active/in-progress Billing Onboarding related to the Combined Funnel.</description>
    <interviewLabel>CF - Zap - {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
    <label>CF - Zap - Webinar 3 Join (Billing)</label>
